# Workflow scripts are passed inline to the Workflow tool; a lone CR byte trips
# its approval-dialog control-char check and causes a spurious permissions panic.
# The repo-root .gitattributes carries the same rule, but it does not travel when
# this plugin is distributed/checked out as a subtree — keep the rule co-located
# with the template so LF is enforced regardless of core.autocrlf on the consumer.
*.workflow.js text eol=lf
